## 🧱 Code Structure & Modularity

- **Never create files longer than 500 lines** - Split into smaller classes or helpers
- **Organize by feature:**
  - **CodeIgniter 3:**
    - `controllers/` - Request handling
    - `models/` - Data access and business logic
    - `views/` - Presentation layer
    - `libraries/` - Reusable classes
    - `helpers/` - Utility functions
  - **Yii Framework:**
    - `controllers/` - Request handling
    - `models/` - Data models and business logic
    - `views/` - Presentation layer
    - `components/` - Reusable components
    - `widgets/` - UI widgets
- **Use namespaces** (Yii Framework) or proper class loading (CodeIgniter 3)
- **Follow framework's autoloading** patterns

